        <mxCell id="KBjdMgGRRg1gwqXxhLQQ-43" value="On client we run https://localhost/8443&lt;div&gt;It connects with server.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;They run TLS handshake to agree on encryption.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Server process it and send HTTP response back to client.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=27;" parent="1" vertex="1">
